R

relax(List<Coord>) - Method in class squidpony.performance.alternate.DijkstraMap
Used in conjunction with methods that depend on finding cover, like findCoveredAttackPath(), this method causes specified safer points to be considered more safe, and will make a pathfinder more likely to enter those places if they were considered dangerous earlier (due to calling deteriorate()).
